    "body": "Thanks Ratan! After going through the JsonRpcMethods, the code seems more readily designed to have this new command added as a Miner rpc method, rather than an admin.  Miner rpc methods have passed in to them the miningCoordinator, which has executor as a member, which in turn holds the gasLimitCalculator where the targetGasLimit is stored.  The admin rpc methods don't seem to have access to the targetGasLimit.  If there is a way to do it through admin rpc methods, it would be a far more round about way compared to miner rpc methods.",
